relation: This is one of my favorite colored pencil pieces. Ness's visit to Magicant was surely saddening to his friends, and I tried to catch that emotion as well as the odd lighting effects.
The Chosen Four during the final battle. Ness deals the final blow to Pokey.
Though I never quite finished EarthBound 0/Mother 1, I still made Giegue, looking rather angrily out of his armored bio-support tank.
An old sketch of Giygas, the cosmic destroyer and party animal.
A pencil sketch of Grapefruit Falls, located just outside of Saturn Valley. Oh the secrets it doth holds...
